Textiles - Carbondale, PA:
Supplier Information & Manual
Interested In Providing Materials and Components?
The Gentex textiles group, located in Carbondale, PA, welcomes the opportunity to work with a wide variety of quality suppliers that provide materials and components used in the manufacture of our products.
To learn more about becoming a supplier to Gentex, please access a copy of our Supplier Performance Management Guide available in Adobe PDF format.
