Industrial Safety











Land & Sea
Gentex’s comprehensive suite of head protection and situational awareness products provide troops on the ground and at sea with industry leading protection and advanced performance.



Dismounted



We design helmets that provide ballistic penetration resistance, impact protection, comfort and stability for the dismounted war fighter.


Select ProductAdvanced Combat Helmet (ACH)
USMC Lightweight Helmet (LWH)
Gentex Tactical Ballistic Helmet (TBH) Systems





Mounted



We provide the ability to communicate via intercom or radios while being afforded ballistic and impact protection with our Gentex vehicle helmet systems.


Select ProductTactical Communications Helmet (TCH) Maritime or Ground Use
Special Operations Headset Adaptable Helmet (SOHAH)





Maritime



Our helmet platforms are designed to withstand the most extreme maritime enviroment while providing ballistic and impact protection available with or without communications.


Select ProductTactical Communications Helmet (TCH), Maritime or Ground Use
Special Operations Headset Adaptable Helmet (SOHAH)
Phonetalker Type III Maritime-Ground Helmet





Law Enforcement



The Gentex family of Law Enforcement helmets are NTOA approved and tested against ballistic threat levels with 9mm and other projectiles.


