GENTEX Corporation - Careers






















HomeOpen PositionsEmployee BenefitsWhy GentexLearn More





HomeWhat We DoLocationsCulture & ValuesHistoryCommunity
  




At Gentex Corporation, we've created an environment where great ideas and great people can thrive. Leveraging a history that spans more than 100 years, Gentex is a global leader in personal protection and situational awareness solutions for defense forces, emergency responders, and industrial personnel operating in high performance environments. Join our multinational team of over 900 exceptional and dedicated employees around the world and work on challenging and rewarding projects, grow your skills, and advance your career. Together, you and Gentex can build a career that's uniquely yours.



 

Experienced Professionals
Further your career with Gentex in an exciting industry and acompany that is dedicated to advancing and growing its employees.



 
 


 

Students & New Graduates
Begin your career with exciting opportunities at Gentex.



 
  


 
Current Employees
Continue to grow your career at Gentex with opportunities toadvance your skills and capabilities.



 
  


 

Transitioning Military
Join a team that values your experience and your commitment to serve.





